{"tid":1562914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先有個傻仔出閘chok柒左","createTime":"2019-09-12T08:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T08:58:57.000Z","uid":283129,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40b4a0a887a7fb0bb21358eb48a00e297acf53cc","tid":1562914,"uid":283129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:06:47.000Z","msg":"冇錯嗰個就係我<br />\n<br />\n通常有部份低調嘅巴打會選擇chok閘出，但係之前有手足爆站嗰陣拆咗個轉閘出嚟，結果新裝返上去嗰啲硬到仆街<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\nchok之前望清楚佢轉軸個位，新嗰啲一眼望到閃好多<br />\n好在我嗰陣冇人望住，如果唔係失敗實俾人睇實<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrom唔夠靈活跳閘嘅柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e628a8b591f14f6ddecf5e9a26c3265bcde070","tid":1562914,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:07:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5798f2b5548b0d42c997f74a8da5b2b4159e90d9","tid":1562914,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:09:18.000Z","msg":"手唔夠力用腳撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6fc51c078bb5435ca7147e305c195de63e2cde","tid":1562914,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime